pull_request.title: Fix test_alg_info.py on Windows platform
pull_request.body:
Fix test_alg_info.py on Windows which cause the ninja run_tests failure.

Since `gerp` is not available on Windows, making use of powershell is a good alternative way to replace grep.

Thanks for fixing this "cut-copy-paste" error!
